text: Roger Heinkelé (6 January 1913 - 24 April 2001) was a French diver. He competed at the 1936 Summer Olympics and the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:2001 deaths Category:French male divers Category:Olympic divers of France Category:Divers at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Divers at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
